 r45842@pinglin:  jesse | 2006-12-06 02:13:13 -0500
 * Added support for:
 
 div {
     attr( id => 'foo');
     
     outs('my text');
 }
     
 In addition to the existing support for:
 
 div {
     {  id is 'foo' }
     
     outs('my text');
 }
     
 Tested both.
 

